==Octavia E. Butler Memorial Scholarship==
The Octavia E. Butler Memorial Scholarship was established in Butler&#x27;s memory in 2006 by the Society. Its goal is to provide an annual scholarship to enable writers of color to attend one of the Clarion writing workshops where Butler got her start. The first scholarship was awarded in 2007.

